John:  Wars are caused by greed, standards are compromise because it is less expensive to operate dangerously rather than under safe and healthy conditions.<br><br>
The same government that sent me to Viet Nam promised to feed my ancestors at Wounded Knee.  The money was appropriated and disbursed... but no food got to my people. When they came pass the point of watching their infants die of starvation they walked away in the cold, freezing winter to find food their own way.  They were slaughtered by irate remnants of the 7th U.S. Cavalry.<br><br>
The &quot;government&quot; does not have a name or a face... no heart and no conscieous.  While we curse the government and shake our fists to no avail, we must remember... that WE are the government.  Where have we failed?  We are lethargic.  We do not vote at all... or we vote for the guy with the prettiest tie.<br><br>
You weren't fired because you were incompetent... you are the victim of greed.<br><br>
They can rob you of your livelihood... but apparently they can not steal your honor.<br><br>
Men of your caliber are needed in other places... I trust that you will find something better... at least you will search with a clear conscience.<br><br>
Life here is short!  Remember, while you are here... &quot;Maka kin le, mitawa ca,&quot;  I own the Earth!<br><br>
Humming Eagle
